 real effort, unlike the investment it takes to genuinely understand a person.', 1456, 0), (245496, 'I would rather die than hate.', 12964, 0), (245497, 'Love me!Hate me!I don''t care which because either way,you''re still talking about me!', 2876, 0), (245498, 'People always seem to band together in accordance to a principle that has nothing to do with love, a principle that releases them from personal responsibility. (p. 81)', 85, 0), (245499, 'Today I was rejected......I hate being rejected... SAYYYYYYYYYY MY FUCKING NAME "Bill".', 4605, 0), (245500, 'Real love does not hurt, but the rotten lies about love can cause you to hate love.', 5160, 0);
